{"tid":376784,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"熊本熊 碗 腐皮烏冬 堅好食 🍜","createTime":"2017-08-27T08:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T04:21:34.000Z","uid":28412,"like":62,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ba17c7e9f8f0b08dd2bec62581d7b431f269c4a","tid":376784,"uid":28412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:48:18.000Z","msg":"經一個前同學介紹，佢話連登仔係咁推呢款烏冬，所以買咗個黎試下，買咗好似$13.5 , 平時不嬲唔多食烏冬，見未試過就試下。<br />\n<br />\n望落都幾大兜下 個兜大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/163359_7c560ed3c598d29cc0a8c42624800bb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F163359_7c560ed3c598d29cc0a8c42624800bb0.jpg&h=3c33a4b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熊本熊塊牌後面有食法 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/163359_1ac382d4e8937981a5f91509bb483893.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F163359_1ac382d4e8937981a5f91509bb483893.jpg&h=36aa1517&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入面有腐皮一塊，湯粉一包，烏冬一包仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/163400_18a09017ac48f7d1c79a9eb9941d7345.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F163400_18a09017ac48f7d1c79a9eb9941d7345.jpg&h=4cbc4a51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/163401_18a09017ac48f7d1c79a9eb9941d7345.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F163401_18a09017ac48f7d1c79a9eb9941d7345.jpg&h=a4abdaf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始落水 浸佢5分鐘 個牌就寫1分鐘，<br />\n落完水真係成個烏冬都係油黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/163402_d124b351c8e9957c7676983ff0b6bf45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F163402_d124b351c8e9957c7676983ff0b6bf45.jpg&h=b439daf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/163442_616f46177b814dd887ca87c6431e53ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F163442_616f46177b814dd887ca87c6431e53ae.jpg&h=7ab83e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n倒完啱啱油浸個啲水 就倒過啲新嘅熱水<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/163443_7935148f69adc2be84e601c4ceadd94b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F163443_7935148f69adc2be84e601c4ceadd94b.jpg&h=60960b73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落埋啲料落去 似返碗烏冬 🍜<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/163443_e3ac1bf3c6de0e288547a75328bf23ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F163443_e3ac1bf3c6de0e288547a75328bf23ac.jpg&h=80e51cff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/163444_e3ac1bf3c6de0e288547a75328bf23ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F163444_e3ac1bf3c6de0e288547a75328bf23ac.jpg&h=7510e55b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啲湯算幾好飲，我落咗一大兜水都唔會話好淡，個湯應該係日本人好中意飲嘅 味噌湯，入面綠色個啲應該海帶，烏冬都算唔錯，塊腐皮甜甜地，第一次食呢隻。<br />\n<br />\n整體黎講 如果10分都有8分，烏冬係比較小，好快就食晒，但碗湯可以慢慢飲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢好似仲有出幾隻味，得閒買埋黎試下，有食過其他味嘅可以分享下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084d3287a2a1e8c7a324e835b1ec46b7ecb25533","tid":376784,"uid":80503,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:50:00.000Z","msg":"份量真係好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859af361e349a6780954017a4e347ce80da74024","tid":376784,"uid":76710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:50:03.000Z","msg":"Ching 不如一日一杯輀評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19f1d1f0d808d7f71d3344aee30b50dcbe87d34","tid":376784,"uid":28412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ching 不如一日一杯輀評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以諗下 之前都未試過杯裝嘅烏冬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32ebc3e48c5e9a23734603aee88d9a694d3d1eb","tid":376784,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:51:14.000Z","msg":"屌 樓主係熊本派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0294a37b52d2bc0131c40119e491435cca2dcad2","tid":376784,"uid":28412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:52:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 樓主係熊本派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩係熊本派 我見隻熊易認 所以講熊本熊烏冬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a19051dc94c483989444256ae4a56c5a1b5eca","tid":376784,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:54:03.000Z","msg":"一田好似11.9 <br />\n但份量真係好小    以前759有隻係可以直接放上爐面煮"},{"pid":"c3a82890750812cec483bf3f172f93092fa03afb","tid":376784,"uid":10788,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:54:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌 樓主係熊本派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩係熊本派 我見隻熊易認 所以講熊本熊烏冬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n[url]我正式宣佈759腐皮烏冬拉麵取代味道合同營多 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/333191?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/333191?ref=ios</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]<br />\n<br />\n我衛兵💂&zwj;♀️派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339e4c5cbf30d424641d610383e368e82a03ad21","tid":376784,"uid":28412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一田好似11.9 <br />\n但份量真係好小    以前759有隻係可以直接放上爐面煮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁平，下次去一田望下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔洗放爐煮其實幾方便 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad4bef8ef9896c12d0c470b866c346a46fec16f","tid":376784,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:56:40.000Z","msg":"5啖食完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6aa74ca37903ab9dc01e0cc6ea5e57587cdc1a2","tid":376784,"uid":28412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:58:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>5啖食完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下次買兩個應該啱啱好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ef7c054f1463ffffca4a165a3688d703e569d2","tid":376784,"uid":29522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:59:46.000Z","msg":"一啲都唔覺得好食 好撚難食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd93e8ef78f356f7bf05892cd4bb3e6f6443477","tid":376784,"uid":29522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:00:34.000Z","msg":"啲湯得個甜字 勁清<br />\n塊腐皮好似食緊糖咁 甜到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8d15c194f1b84df516eacec0177c6109b575fd","tid":376784,"uid":28412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:03:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲湯得個甜字 勁清<br />\n塊腐皮好似食緊糖咁 甜到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n腐皮甜 可能本身都係甜，<br />\n個湯都唔算甜，同日本飲個啲差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f490f0e36a28e181fa28cfd78e77312840fb3c","tid":376784,"uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:05:16.000Z","msg":"試多啲其他日本杯麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲個樣好似好吸引 但又驚中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318be9cc800f4a69c5b6fce6fd97238d793f7099","tid":376784,"uid":28412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:09:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試多啲其他日本杯麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲個樣好似好吸引 但又驚中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得閒再睇下 再影相寫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82a5ff0477d2f62688889207c8624caf0493cd7","tid":376784,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:47:58.000Z","msg":"塊腐皮甜甜地，第一次食呢隻<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c54f96b6f349bf5a4e72a5c6badcd38903449eb","tid":376784,"uid":10019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:53:14.000Z","msg":"邊到買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ceee0974b69d5dd3e15fca13c4bbd335b65f4ac","tid":376784,"uid":28412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:01:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊到買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一田有"},{"pid":"be6f74ff8cb9e3a6fa41957ac5d566dca2164a0c","tid":376784,"uid":28412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-2